---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import DocsSidebar from "../../components/DocsSidebar.astro";
---
<Layout title="MCP server · flipagent docs">
	<div class="cmw cmw-bordered">
		<div class="docs-shell">
			<DocsSidebar />
			<article class="docs-content">
				<h1>MCP server</h1>
				<p class="lead">flipagent-mcp is a Model Context Protocol server that exposes the full reseller API as MCP tools. Works with any compatible AI client: Claude Desktop, Cursor, Cline, Zed, Windsurf.</p>

				<h2>Install</h2>
				<p>The MCP server is published on npm and runs through <code>npx</code>, so no global install is needed. The fastest path is the CLI:</p>
				<div class="code"><pre><code>{`npx -y flipagent-cli init --mcp`}</code></pre></div>
				<p>It auto-detects every supported client and writes the config in one go.</p>

				<h2>Claude Desktop (manual)</h2>
				<p>Edit <code>~/Library/Application Support/Claude/claude_desktop_config.json</code>:</p>
				<div class="code"><pre><code>{`{
  "mcpServers": {
    "flipagent": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "flipagent-mcp"],
      "env": { "FLIPAGENT_API_KEY": "fa_free_xxx" }
    }
  }
}`}</code></pre></div>
				<p>Restart Claude. The tools below show up in any chat.</p>

				<h2>Cursor / Cline / Zed / Windsurf</h2>
				<p>Same JSON, different file:</p>
				<table class="api">
					<thead><tr><th>Client</th><th>Config file</th></tr></thead>
					<tbody>
						<tr><td>Cursor</td><td><code>.cursor/mcp.json</code> (in workspace)</td></tr>
						<tr><td>Cline</td><td><code>~/.cline/mcp.json</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td>Zed</td><td>Settings → MCP servers</td></tr>
						<tr><td>Windsurf</td><td>Settings → Cascade → MCP servers</td></tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>

				<h2>Tools exposed (108)</h2>
				<p>Tool names follow <code>flipagent_&lt;resource&gt;_&lt;verb&gt;</code>, mirroring <code>/v1/&lt;resource&gt;/&lt;verb&gt;</code> and the <code>client.&lt;resource&gt;.&lt;verb&gt;()</code> SDK shape (dots become underscores). Marketplace stays a parameter — the same tools work as Amazon and Mercari adapters land.</p>

				<table class="api">
					<thead><tr><th>Tool</th><th>Backed by</th></tr></thead>
					<tbody>
						<tr><td colspan="2"><strong>Marketplace data &mdash; read</strong></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_items_search</code></td><td><code>GET /v1/items/search</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_items_get</code></td><td><code>GET /v1/items/&#123;id&#125;</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_items_search_sold</code></td><td><code>GET /v1/items/search?status=sold</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_categories_list</code></td><td><code>GET /v1/categories?parentId=&#123;?&#125;</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_categories_suggest</code></td><td><code>GET /v1/categories/suggest</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_categories_aspects</code></td><td><code>GET /v1/categories/&#123;id&#125;/aspects</code></td></tr>

						<tr><td colspan="2"><strong>Decisions</strong></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_evaluate</code></td><td><code>POST /v1/evaluate</code> &mdash; composite (search + LLM same-product filter + score)</td></tr>

						<tr><td colspan="2"><strong>Operations</strong> (ship + expenses + forwarder)</td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_ship_quote</code> / <code>_providers</code></td><td><code>POST /v1/ship/quote</code> &middot; <code>GET /v1/ship/providers</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_expenses_record</code> / <code>_summary</code></td><td><code>POST /v1/expenses/record</code> &middot; <code>GET /v1/expenses/summary</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_forwarder_refresh</code> / <code>_packages_photos</code> / <code>_packages_dispatch</code> / <code>_packages_link</code> / <code>_inventory_list</code> / <code>_jobs_get</code></td><td><code>/v1/forwarder/&#123;provider&#125;/*</code> (Planet Express today)</td></tr>

						<tr><td colspan="2"><strong>Buy</strong> (REST or bridge)</td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_purchases_create</code> / <code>_get</code> / <code>_cancel</code></td><td><code>/v1/purchases/*</code></td></tr>

						<tr><td colspan="2"><strong>Listing prerequisites</strong> (run these before <code>listings_create</code>)</td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_media_create_upload</code> / <code>_get</code></td><td><code>/v1/media/*</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_policies_list</code> / <code>_list_by_type</code></td><td><code>/v1/policies/*</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_locations_list</code> / <code>_get</code> / <code>_upsert</code> / <code>_delete</code> / <code>_enable</code> / <code>_disable</code></td><td><code>/v1/locations/*</code></td></tr>

						<tr><td colspan="2"><strong>Sell-side</strong> (eBay OAuth required via <code>/v1/connect/ebay</code>)</td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_connect_ebay_status</code></td><td><code>GET /v1/connect/ebay/status</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_listings_create</code> / <code>_update</code> / <code>_relist</code></td><td><code>/v1/listings/*</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_listing_groups_get</code> / <code>_upsert</code> / <code>_delete</code></td><td><code>/v1/listing-groups/*</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_listings_bulk_get_inventory</code> / <code>_get_offers</code> / <code>_update_prices</code> / <code>_upsert</code> / <code>_publish</code> / <code>_migrate</code></td><td><code>/v1/listings/bulk/*</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_sales_list</code> / <code>_ship</code></td><td><code>/v1/sales/*</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_payouts_list</code></td><td><code>GET /v1/payouts</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_transactions_list</code></td><td><code>GET /v1/transactions</code></td></tr>

						<tr><td colspan="2"><strong>Buyer comms + post-sale</strong></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_messages_list</code> / <code>_send</code></td><td><code>/v1/messages</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_offers_list</code> / <code>_create</code> / <code>_eligible_listings</code> / <code>_respond</code></td><td><code>/v1/offers/*</code> (Best Offer)</td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_disputes_list</code> / <code>_get</code> / <code>_respond</code></td><td><code>/v1/disputes/*</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_feedback_list</code> / <code>_awaiting</code> / <code>_leave</code></td><td><code>/v1/feedback/*</code></td></tr>

						<tr><td colspan="2"><strong>Sourcing radar + auctions</strong></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_watching_list</code> / <code>_watch</code> / <code>_unwatch</code></td><td><code>/v1/watching/*</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_saved_searches_list</code> / <code>_create</code> / <code>_delete</code></td><td><code>/v1/saved-searches/*</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_trends_categories</code></td><td><code>GET /v1/trends/categories</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_recommendations_list</code></td><td><code>GET /v1/recommendations</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_bids_list</code> / <code>_place</code> / <code>_eligible_listings</code></td><td><code>/v1/bids/*</code></td></tr>

						<tr><td colspan="2"><strong>Seller account</strong> (read-only)</td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_seller_eligibility</code> / <code>_privilege</code> / <code>_kyc</code> / <code>_subscription</code> / <code>_payments_program</code> / <code>_advertising_eligibility</code> / <code>_sales_tax</code></td><td><code>/v1/me/seller/*</code></td></tr>

						<tr><td colspan="2"><strong>Marketing + storefront</strong></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_promotions_list</code> / <code>_create</code> / <code>_reports_*</code></td><td><code>/v1/promotions/*</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_markdowns_list</code> / <code>_create</code></td><td><code>/v1/markdowns</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_ads_campaigns_*</code> / <code>_ads_list</code> / <code>_groups_*</code> / <code>_reports_*</code></td><td><code>/v1/ads/*</code> (Promoted Listings)</td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_store_categories</code> / <code>_categories_upsert</code></td><td><code>/v1/store/categories</code></td></tr>

						<tr><td colspan="2"><strong>Setup</strong> (webhooks, notifications, key info, capabilities)</td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_capabilities</code></td><td><code>GET /v1/capabilities</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_keys_me</code></td><td><code>GET /v1/keys/me</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_webhooks_register</code> / <code>_list</code> / <code>_revoke</code></td><td><code>/v1/webhooks/*</code></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_notifications_topics</code> / <code>_destinations</code> / <code>_subscriptions_*</code> / <code>_recent</code></td><td><code>/v1/notifications/*</code></td></tr>

						<tr><td colspan="2"><strong>Generic browser primitives</strong></td></tr>
						<tr><td><code>flipagent_browser_query</code></td><td><code>POST /v1/browser/query</code></td></tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>

				<h2>Compose your own logic</h2>
				<p>Tools are typed and orthogonal. <code>flipagent_evaluate</code> is composite — server-side it fetches the item, searches sold + active, runs an LLM same-product filter, and scores in a single call. Agents can also chain low-level tools (<code>flipagent_items_search</code> → <code>flipagent_items_search_sold</code> → <code>flipagent_evaluate</code> → <code>flipagent_ship_quote</code>) to assemble custom reselling workflows. See the <a href="/docs/api/">API reference</a> for request shapes.</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
